dxcluster-scraper (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * BREAKING: Replaced deprecated telnetlib with socket module
  * Improved connection reliability and error handling
  * Better timeout management and reconnection logic
  * Removed dependency on python3-telnetlib3
  * Compatible with Python 3.11+ where telnetlib is not available

 -- Steve Buer <steve@example.com>  Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:00:00 -0800

dxcluster-scraper (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of DX Cluster Scraper service package
  * Telnet-based DX cluster monitoring and data collection
  * PostgreSQL database integration for spot storage
  * Systemd service configuration for production deployment
  * Service management scripts and utilities
  * Automatic user and directory setup

